{"tid":1675581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我屌哂你地成班當手足係condom既仆街！","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T08:48:56.000Z","uid":285622,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"802790bcc10ee6a755ef34bc213316e053dc37a2","tid":1675581,"uid":285622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"有流亡台灣既手足行出黎，話同佢既團隊第一身接觸到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新屋嶺被輪姦受害者同佢既家屬</span></strong></span><br />\n講埋細節<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>國中生（初中）</strong></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4狗輪姦 自殺4次</strong></span></span><br />\n仲講埋被自殺者家屬<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被警方恐嚇滅聲</span></span><br />\n佢行出黎講 隨時連命都冇埋 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單野其實好核彈 但單野竟然尋日到宜家都上唔撚到熱門</strong></span></span><br />\n如果大家唔focus係件事上邊 份份鐘連手足家屬都死撚埋 係咪要女手足自己行上台講自己俾人輪足一晚你地先肯理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>係咪要當被輪姦既女手足係condom?!<br />\n係咪要當被自殺既手足係condom?!<br />\n係咪要當係台灣爆料既手足係condom?!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n單野上唔到熱門既連登可以摺埋<br />\n